 Because they're your friend you can trust that they will treat you fair and do a good job vs a stranger. But it doesn't mean it should be a free job. Something simple sometimes a few beers are enough but always offer a fair rate if you don't want them to start avoiding you. Also don't only call them when you need something, that's not a real friendship.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/DOhiKDv</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[researchonyourown]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>America’s first successful FBI whistleblower, Dr. Frederic Whitehurst, changed the U.S. criminal justice system forever.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/8TNdUZq</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XbmpPJ5.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/U2QsjjH.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CcWlyIQ.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KqJy2Og.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pJiwCr1.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YJfSAW5.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>source: https://whistleblowersblog.org/government-whistleblowers/intelligence-community-whistleblowers/dr-whitehurst-and-the-fbi-lab-scandal/</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/8TNdUZq</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[theshopliftingseagull]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>MLB Batter Killed by Wild Pitch</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/6FVLYp0</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xLdUwvb.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Second baseman Dee Strange-Gordon kills